Refrigerate Loop Exit Test.

This tests using Refrigerate as a conditional early exit inside a loop.
If the condition is non-zero, Refrigerate exits immediately with output.
If zero, execution continues past the loop.

Ingredients.
3 g counter
5 g result

Method.
Put result into mixing bowl.
Pour contents of the mixing bowl into the baking dish.
Check the counter.
Put counter into mixing bowl.
Refrigerate for 1 hours.
Check the counter until checked.

Serves 1.
